      "application": "Technical→technical_detail. Ethical→ethical_reasoning. High_stakes→full_audit_trail.",
      "balance": "Transparency≠overwhelming_detail. Match_disclosure_to_stakes_and_audience.",
      "relates": ["S0", "G2"]
    },
